{"word":"G1842 - ἐξολοθρεύω - exolothreúō - ex-ol-oth-ryoo'-o - Destroy","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξολοθρεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exolothreúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-ol-oth-ryoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Destroy</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிர்மூலமாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to destroy out of its place, destroy utterly, to extirpate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G3645 - ὀλοθρεύω - olothreúō - ol-oth-ryoo'-o/3645\">G3645</a>; to <i>extirpate:</i> - destroy.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1842/1842\">G1842</a>, <a href=\"#/G3639/3639\">G3639</a>, <a href=\"#/G3644/3644\">G3644</a>, <a href=\"#/G3645/3645\">G3645</a>"}]}